Package: bdrc
Title: Bayesian Discharge Rating Curves
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: c(person("Birgir", "Hrafnkelsson", email = "birgirhr@hi.is", role = c("aut","cph")),
             person("Solvi", "Rognvaldsson", email = "solviro@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"),comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-4376-3361")),
             person("Axel Orn", "Jansson", email = "axelorn94@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
             person("Rafael", "Vias", email = "raffidv@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
             )
Description: Fits a discharge rating curve from paired stage and discharge measurements in a river using a Bayesian hierarchical model. The package implements four different models, two power-law rating curves and two generalized power-law rating curves as described in Hrafnkelsson et al (2020) <arXiv:2010.04769>.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
